<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-surface via-surface/90 to-transparent z-10"></div>
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center" data-alt="A cinematic, wide-angle shot of a sun-drenched Indonesian coffee plantation at dawn. Lush emerald green coffee trees laden with ripe red cherries stretch across rolling hills under a soft golden mist. The lighting is ethereal and premium, reflecting a high-end corporate agribusiness aesthetic with deep greens and warm earthy tones. The atmosphere is professional, serene, and abundant." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC7WQsW9wuFPyzfl7BFc6wt82qEtqk7gGYDxAcurD1f75-B5OTajq0aZkVnevvGMFzAg3BqmiFO6ZZTscYSekkkPHWOBJRd30bArDlMMlu7O5u5lRiEOdHklLO_Wo3TY6eaJ9gkd3aR__VBE-3XP73ne4U2hQJQJze3zl_APnCyLrIzLlVYWW5aO0uTRNhCseLPnSOZAw0s4Q2g3fgRzq304RpEmdIdHYS398u3G7eVHSnDxuFu44ATbd-qv0sSscqU28T3CrYD222I"/>
</div>
<div class="container mx-auto px-margin-desktop relative z-20 max-w-container-max">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed rounded-full mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">verified</span>
<span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Verified Export Partner</span>
</div>
<h1 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-on-surface mb-6 leading-tight">
                        Bridging Indonesian Agribusiness to the <span class="text-primary">Global Market.</span>
</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-lg">
                        Empowering UMKM exporters with a high-touch trading platform designed for scale, transparency, and global trust.
                    </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<button class="px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-xl font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all">
                            Start Trading Now
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_flat</span>
</button>
<button class="px-8 py-4 bg-white border border-outline-variant text-on-surface rounded-xl font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                            Explore Marketplace
                        </button>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-8">
<div>
<p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">500+</p>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-secondary uppercase">Verified Sellers</p>
</div>
<div class="w-px h-10 bg-outline-variant"></div>
<div>
<p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">$12M+</p>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-secondary uppercase">Trade Volume</p>
</div>
<div class="w-px h-10 bg-outline-variant"></div>
<div>
<p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary">15+</p>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-secondary uppercase">Countries</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- How It Works -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface">
<div class="container mx-auto px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-4">How it Works</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">Our streamlined process ensures every transaction is secure, verified, and efficient from inquiry to delivery.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
<!-- Connector line for desktop -->
<div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-primary/40 to-primary/10 -translate-y-12"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 group">
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">request_quote</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-3 text-on-surface">1. RFQ</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Post your Request for Quotation or browse existing requirements from international buyers.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 group">
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">gavel</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-3 text-on-surface">2. Bidding</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Engage in transparent bidding. Negotiate terms directly with verified exporters to get the best value.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 group">
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary transition-colors h-full flex flex-col items-center text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">handshake</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-3 text-on-surface">3. Handover</h3>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Finalize logistics and trade finance. Secure escrow payment and tracked international shipping.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Featured Commodities (Bento Grid) -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="container mx-auto px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
<div>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-2">Featured Commodities</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Premium Indonesian exports sourced directly from origin.</p>
</div>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-2 transition-all">
                        View All Commodities <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span>
</button>
</div>
<div class="bento-grid">
<!-- Big Card -->
<div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl min-h-[400px]">
<img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="Close-up macro photography of high-quality Indonesian Arabica coffee beans. The beans are rich, dark brown with a subtle oily sheen, displayed in a rustic wooden bowl. The lighting is dramatic and warm, highlighting the textures and premium nature of the produce. Deep forest green and golden amber accents define the color palette, suggesting luxury and authenticity." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBeaLVYKfRZeadpeekV7M8txPHA0H1jwLXkGLl8F54nrQzyn3clu1BEwO247ADA6_HOxNM21QTZGedXm_J-qNRVX9nELZ1FsUAh387rBdTQlWhNisUPGSp6d629_uz1sSzTYfHggR8KZm_S6evKp32zp5v7cug2P3JMZ6GQoK4qe7r9rbWJIWD7QpcgteYF_snw2NS5SfcyPh5lmM4zPxUn6qAqEc3aV1RTBWFyg0Tyc1sh0luqYz6HLNdYMJuIDI-AsOZaYnrdJ5UW"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-10">
<span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-glow text-white rounded-full font-label-sm text-label-sm mb-4 w-fit">Top Export</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-white mb-2">Sumatra Mandheling Coffee</h3>
<p class="text-white/80 font-body-md max-w-md">Renowned for its smooth body and earthy notes. Sourced from smallholder farmers in North Sumatra.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Small Card 1 -->
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl min-h-[400px]">
<img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="An artistic arrangement of various Indonesian spices including cloves, nutmeg, and cinnamon sticks on a dark stone surface. The spices are vibrant and richly colored, lit with sharp side lighting to emphasize their intricate textures. The mood is sophisticated and culinary, emphasizing the heritage of the Spice Islands. A professional, high-contrast digital look with deep earthy browns and warm yellows." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBsj62zXhti37XhyAj9CS3bGLdVXGeYES8FRjCv2zmv-lyGgy5dxBe-wlBlnkr6QvswoFA5YOsU6i6P193EBdrAzYslysjgLTN_TAzRESqI8-xx8y3KqXFR6yIvIs_1u25oCuFATO4_g8_dU8PbQebnNgZ5TjaRqmutiKqoYIYWFJSXxC9UQLE5L2pPEtvJH2B7INRcdHiRrT8csUU36Uy0xN8iZTgknJZtp-EIper2-QgvtSe5-LL0b6d9e1dR4UbcCGl2MqjTYvU-"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white mb-1">Organic Spices</h3>
<p class="text-white/80 font-body-sm">Cloves, Nutmeg, and Mace from the Maluku Islands.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Small Card 2 -->
<div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl min-h-[300px]">
<img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="A sun-bleached heap of high-grade Cashew nuts being dried on a woven mat in a tropical setting. The image uses high-key, natural lighting to create a clean and healthy aesthetic. Soft neutral tones of beige and cream dominate the scene, with lush tropical greenery blurred in the background. The style is modern, professional, and food-safe." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDmdFRj-HA7oNI-2Kv4UWfDiOLP4_ILD9A62UoPGYFYVSxXbWLN21_zqdWSwzGcJ2wHpRrJlFmAGlV5bbUoU5v3_2nt1XrGx5Bsxcv43aeGzotVhvHo8vU0s0e1F1OpiqH8Ih_iy5nAsQA7IqHeBMa0PSTVgl6uYvfAYhjnNAgFcUNLvRhyCAxq0ojJ952iYjUtmUvdeZZcYgqk8OME7WcxbTpmMwaiNBJ72C1wnqqjktUXOAjSmkIXN0Y-GYyLOrjf7WNSNzerDhE-"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white mb-1">Premium Cashews</h3>
<p class="text-white/80 font-body-sm">Export-grade kernels from Southeast Sulawesi.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- CTA Card -->
<div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 bg-primary-container p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-glow/10 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<h3 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-primary-container mb-4">Can't find what you're looking for?</h3>
<p class="text-on-primary-container/80 font-body-md max-w-lg mb-0">Post a specific RFQ and let our network of 500+ verified Indonesian suppliers reach out to you with competitive quotes.</p>
</div>
<button class="relative z-10 whitespace-nowrap px-8 py-4 bg-antique-base text-primary font-label-md text-label-md rounded-xl hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-xl">
                            Post New RFQ
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Trust & Security -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface overflow-hidden">
<div class="container mx-auto px-margin-desktop max-w-container-max">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div>
<div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-verification-blue/10 text-verification-blue rounded-full font-label-sm text-label-sm mb-6">Built for Reliability</div>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-6">Uncompromising Trust &amp; Security</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10">We eliminate the risks of cross-border trade through a systematic trust framework that protects both buyers and sellers at every milestone.</p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
<div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-white shadow-sm border border-outline-variant rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">verified_user</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-1">Multi-Layer KYC</h4>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Every exporter undergoes rigorous identity, legal, and operational verification before joining the platform.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
<div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-white shadow-sm border border-outline-variant rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">policy</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-1">Trade Insurance</h4>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Optional comprehensive cargo and credit insurance to safeguard your investments against unforeseen disruptions.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors">
<div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-white shadow-sm border border-outline-variant rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">payments</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-1">Escrow Protection</h4>
<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant">Funds are held securely in escrow and only released when predefined delivery and quality milestones are met.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative glass-card p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-outline-variant">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
<h5 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Verification Status</h5>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">security</span>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-surface rounded-xl border border-emerald-glow/20">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-glow"></div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md">Exporter License</span>
</div>
<span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-emerald-glow flex items-center gap-1"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">check_circle</span> Verified</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-surface rounded-xl border border-emerald-glow/20">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-glow"></div>
